    "bullets": [
      "Firms identified through a novel patent-based measure of AI use in their innovation process, splitting green from non-green firms; period, geography, and sample size are not stated.",
      "The paper measures firms' adoption of AI, particularly generative AI, from patent data rather than running a named model, and establishes causality with a difference-in-differences design.",
      "Green firms raise green innovation output by about 15 to 24 percent after adopting AI and improve innovation quality, though profitability gains stay limited by higher associated costs."
    ],
